Title: Medical Outreach Mission
Description: Assist doctors and nurses in providing free medical checkups, basic medicines, and health education to residents in need.
Location: Carcar City Health Center, Carcar, Cebu

Title: Mountain Trail Clean and Trek
Description: A day-long activity combining mountain hiking with trail cleanup efforts to keep Cebu's scenic mountain routes safe and clean.

Title: Barangay Literacy Day
Description: Assist in reading activities, storytelling sessions, and simple tutoring for young learners.
Location: Barangay Tipolo Community Center, Mandaue City, Cebu

Title: Wildlife Awareness Camp
Description: Assist in youth camps teaching wildlife protection and biodiversity conservation.
Location: Cebu Safari and Adventure Park, Barangay Corte, Toril, Carmen, Cebu

Title: Disaster Preparedness Training Assistance
Description: Provide support during drills and assist trainers in coordinating residents.
Location: Naga City Disaster Risk Reduction Center, Naga City, Cebu
